Meet the BANDIT
===============

The "Build AND Install Toolkit", BANDIT, is the tool for installing a phyglos distribution. 

The INSTALL file describes how to install BANDIT in the HOST system. 

The RAISE file describes a quick way to raise a phyglos machine from the HOST system using BANDIT. 

Visit http://phy.wiki for more details and other installation methods.


